Class AbstractHTMLControlTag<T extends Control>

java.lang.Object
  javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.TagSupport
      org.jcatapult.mvc.result.jsp.AbstractControlTag<T>
          org.jcatapult.mvc.result.form.jsp.AbstractHTMLControlTag<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, DynamicAttributes, IterationTag, JspTag, Tag
public abstract class AbstractHTMLControlTag<T extends Control>
extends AbstractControlTag<T>

This class is the abstract control tag for the majority of the HTML controls. This class is simple in that it just collects the tag attributes from the JSP and passes them along to the correct implementation of the Control interface.

See Also:
Serialized Form
